.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
5 different games are played: chess, billiard, poker, snooker, backgammon
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, software-developer, journalist, manager
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, ship, tram, jet-ski
House: palace, townhouse, art-deco, cottage, tower
There 5 different types of food: orange, eggplant, peas, cucumber, artichoke

1. the scientist is the person playing chess
2. the analyst is the person eating orange
3. the palace house is the person playing billiard
4. the software-developer is the townhouse house
5. the person playing billiard is to the right of the person playing poker
6. the person driving the train is the person eating artichoke
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person playing snooker
8. the art-deco house is in the middle
9. the journalist is on the far left
10. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant
11. the person driving the snowmobile is to the left or right of the person eating cucumber
12. the person driving the tram is the cottage house
13. the manager is the person driving the jet-ski
14. the journalist is to the left or right of the person playing backgammon

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   journalist	|    software-developer	|     scientist	|    analyst	|    manager	|
| Game		|    snooker	|      backgammon	|      chess	|     poker	|     billiard	|
| House	|     tower	|      townhouse	|      art-deco	| cottage	|     palace	|
| Transport		|     snowmobile	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tram	|   parliament	|
| Food		|     eggplant	|     cucumber	|     artichoke	|     orange	|     peas	|
